    "Kernel ridge regression provides an efficient closed-form solution, dispensing with the necessity for iterative computations in updating the relay model and resulting in faster convergence speeds.",
    "Distribution matching.",
    "Besides the gradient matching and kernel ridge regression, distribution matching changes the optimization principle towards approximating the original graph in the feature space, attracting significant attention in efficient GC studies.",
